# Manda Backoffice — Architecture Decision Record

**Version:** 1.0 — MVP (auth + shell)
**Status:** In development
**Audience:** Engineers and AI agents working on `backoffice/`

> **Scope:** Electron desktop app for Manda staff/ops. Consumes **`/staff/auth/*`** only in this phase — KYC and transactions are deferred. Relevant when working under `src/**`, `electron/**`, or build config.

Workspace-global rules (security, TDD, backend contract) live in `../../AGENTS.md`.

---

## 1. Context and Goals

The backoffice is a **desktop Electron app** for internal operations staff — KYC review, transaction monitoring, and related ops workflows (phased). It is **not** the end-user mobile client (`manda-app/`).

| Concern           | Decision                                                                    |
| ----------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Target            | Desktop (Linux / macOS / Windows) via Electron                              |
| Backend           | `manda` api service on port 3000 — staff JWT namespace (`STAFF_JWT_SECRET`) |
| Phase C (current) | Staff auth flow + minimal authenticated shell only                          |
| Deferred          | KYC queue/detail, transaction list/detail, search, ops actions              |

---

## 2. Architectural Decisions

| Decision        | Choice                                            | Rationale                                                       |
| --------------- | ------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Shell           | Electron 39 + electron-vite 4                     | Native desktop; Vite HMR for renderer                           |
| UI              | React 19 + TypeScript strict                      | Same mental model as mobile client                              |
| Routing         | `react-router-dom` v7 (`createBrowserRouter`)     | Guards for `/login` vs protected `/`                            |
| Server state    | TanStack Query v5                                 | Mirrors `manda-app` retry/stale defaults                        |
| HTTP            | Axios + interceptors in `shared/api/client.ts`    | Single-flight staff refresh on 401                              |
| Token storage   | Electron `safeStorage` via preload IPC            | OS keychain-backed; renderer never touches raw files            |
| Styling         | **CSS modules** + `:root` tokens in `global.css`  | No inline `style` except dynamic CSS vars (e.g. avatar palette) |
| Fonts           | `@fontsource/plus-jakarta-sans` (400/600/700/800) | Loaded in `main.tsx`                                            |
| Path alias      | `@/*` → `src/*`                                   | Enforced by `tsconfig.json`                                     |
| Package manager | npm                                               | Backend monorepo uses pnpm — don't mix inside backoffice        |

