## 4. Electron Security (non-negotiable)

| Control           | Implementation                                                                             |
| ----------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Context isolation | `contextIsolation: true`, `nodeIntegration: false`                                         |
| Renderer sandbox  | `sandbox: true` in `webPreferences`                                                        |
| Preload surface   | Only `window.staffStorage.load/save/clear` — no raw `fs`/`process` in renderer             |
| Token persistence | Main process encrypts with `safeStorage` → `userData/staff-tokens.json` (mode `0600`)      |
| Dev on Linux      | `npm run dev` uses `--noSandbox` (electron-vite) when setuid chrome-sandbox is unavailable |
| Production API    | `VITE_API_URL` must be `https://` — enforced at boot in `shared/api/client.ts`             |

---

## 5. Routing Model

| Path     | Guard                                                 | Page                         |
| -------- | ----------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `/login` | `GuestGuard` → redirect to `/` if authenticated       | `LoginPage`                  |
| `/`      | `AuthGuard` → redirect to `/login` if unauthenticated | `HomePage` inside `AppShell` |
| `*`      | —                                                     | redirect to `/`              |

**Provider order in `App.tsx`:**

```
QueryClientProvider
  └── AuthProvider
       └── SplashGate          // blocks until bootstrapped
            └── RouterProvider
```

